    <p class="lede">Gaggenau is BSH Hausgeräte's ultra-luxury brand — sibling to Bosch (premium) and Thermador (pro-style luxury) under the BSH German portfolio (wholly owned by Bosch since 2015). Our LA Gaggenau oven service benefits from the same <b>BSH Irvine CA parts chain</b> that gives Bosch + Thermador their LA-local service advantage — ~40 miles from most LA service addresses, next-day or same-day parts on ~85% of Gaggenau service calls. Coverage includes the full lineup: <b>400 Series</b> (flagship with hand-brushed stainless, side-opening option, full Combi-Steam functionality, maximum cavity size) and <b>200 Series</b> (entry ultra-luxury, simpler finish + standard features). Product formats include <b>built-in ovens</b>, <b>Combi-Steam hybrid</b> (400 Series), <b>Speed Microwave + Convection</b>, and <b>Warming Drawer</b>. Flush-mount service + BSH Home Connect pairing + Combi-Steam descaling (annual preventive in LA hard water) are the Gaggenau-specific skill areas. Same-day dispatch. $89 residential diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
