    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Side-opening door hinge (400 Series)</h3><p>Specialty hinge architecture. Hinge pair $585-$785. Heavier than standard drop-down; service requires 2-technician handling on some installs.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Touch panel graphical display</h3><p>400 Series touch panel $525-$725. Full graphical display with hand-brushed-metal bezel integration. Restoration includes panel alignment to spec after replacement.</p></div>
